ChartMember.Label: Commitments Met w o SCxx Report Reasons

ChartAxisTitle.Caption: 3 Days to Report is the Target

ChartItemInLegend.LegendText: Reports Completed Within World Class Standard (3 Days)
Reports Not Meeting Standard But Completed On Time

Query.CommandText: SELECT dashboard_report_data.GeoName FROM dashboard_report_data WHERE dashboard_report_data.regionref = 3 AND dashboard_report_data.GeoType = 'C' GROUP BY dashboard_report_data.GeoName ORDER BY dashboard_report_data.GeoName;

SELECT TOP (100) PERCENT dashboard_report_data.Year_Month, dashboard_report_data.Yr, dashboard_report_data.Mo, dashboard_report_data.Country AS GeoName, dashboard_report_data.[Scheduled Tasks], dashboard_report_data.[Ad Hoc Tasks], dashboard_report_data.[Delivered Reports], dashboard_report_data.[Service Visit Not Performed] AS [Commitments Met w/o SCxx Report (Reasons)], dashboard_report_data.[Not Delivered] AS [Commitments Not Delivered], dashboard_report_data.AMs, dashboard_report_data.Accts AS Accounts, dashboard_report_data.Country_ID, [Service Days Country Summary].DaysOnSite, [Service Days Country Summary].DaysToReport, [Service Days Country Summary].[Standard Met?], [Service Days Country Summary].[Additional On Time], [Service Days Country Summary].[Additional Overdue] FROM (SELECT TOP (100) PERCENT SUM(dbo.service_tasks.isautotask) AS [Scheduled Tasks], SUM(CASE WHEN dbo.service_tasks.isautotask = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Ad Hoc Tasks], SUM(CASE WHEN completion_date <= CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) AND service_not_performed = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Delivered Reports], SUM(CASE WHEN (completion_date > CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) OR completion_date IS NULL) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Not Delivered], SUM(CASE WHEN completion_date <= CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) AND service_not_performed > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Service Visit Not Performed], COUNT(DISTINCT dbo.service_tasks.assignedto) AS AMs, COUNT(DISTINCT dbo.service_tasks.productionfacility_ref) AS Accts, RIGHT(CONVERT(VARCHAR(6), dbo.service_tasks.taskdate, 106), 3) + ' ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)) AS Year_Month, MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate) AS Mo, YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate) AS Yr, dbo.country.Country, dbo.country.ID AS Country_ID FROM dbo.service_tasks INNER JOIN dbo.productionfacility ON dbo.service_tasks.productionfacility_ref = dbo.productionfacility.ProductionFacilityRef INNER JOIN dbo.country ON dbo.productionfacility.service_country = dbo.country.ID WHERE (dbo.service_tasks.is_service_task = 1) AND (dbo.service_tasks.taskdate BETWEEN CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, - 12, GETDATE()))) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, - 12, GETDATE()))), 101) AND DATEADD(d, - 1, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(GETDATE())) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(GETDATE())))) AND (dbo.service_tasks.taskdate + dbo.service_tasks.grace_val BETWEEN dbo.service_tasks.taskdate AND DATEADD(d, 30, CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)), 101))) AND (dbo.country.Country = @CountryName) GROUP BY MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate), RIGHT(CONVERT(VARCHAR(6), dbo.service_tasks.taskdate, 106), 3) + ' ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)), dbo.country.Country, dbo.country.ID) AS dashboard_report_data LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT TOP (100) PERCENT AVG([Service Days]) AS DaysOnSite, AVG([Report Days]) AS DaysToReport, ID, SUM(CASE WHEN [Report Days] <= 3 AND Timely = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Standard Met?], SUM(CASE WHEN [Report Days] > 3 AND Timely = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Additional On Time], SUM(CASE WHEN Timely = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Additional Overdue], Yr, Mo FROM (SELECT CAST(COUNT(dbo.servicedate.servicedate_ref) AS DECIMAL(6, 4)) AS [Service Days], DATEDIFF(d, MAX(dbo.servicedate.servicedate_date), service_tasks_5.completion_date) / 1.0000 AS [Report Days], country_4.ID, (CASE WHEN service_tasks_5.completion_date <= service_tasks_5.taskdate + service_tasks_5.grace_val OR service_tasks_5.completion_date <= service_tasks_5.taskdate + 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Timely, MONTH(service_tasks_5.taskdate) AS Mo, YEAR(service_tasks_5.taskdate) AS Yr FROM dbo.servicedate INNER JOIN dbo.service_report ON dbo.servicedate.servicedate_serviceref = dbo.service_report.service_ref INNER JOIN dbo.service_tasks AS service_tasks_5 ON dbo.service_report.service_ref = service_tasks_5.service_ref INNER JOIN dbo.productionfacility AS productionfacility_3 ON service_tasks_5.productionfacility_ref = productionfacility_3.ProductionFacilityRef INNER JOIN dbo.country AS country_4 ON productionfacility_3.service_country = country_4.ID WHERE (service_tasks_5.taskdate BETWEEN CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, - 12, GETDATE()))) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, - 12, GETDATE()))) AND DATEADD(d, - 1, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(GETDATE())) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(GETDATE())))) AND (service_tasks_5.is_service_task = 1) AND (service_tasks_5.taskdate + service_tasks_5.grace_val BETWEEN service_tasks_5.taskdate AND DATEADD(d, 30, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(service_tasks_5.taskdate)) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(service_tasks_5.taskdate)))) AND (service_tasks_5.taskstatusref = 3) AND (country_4.Country = @CountryName) AND (service_tasks_5.service_not_performed = 0) AND (service_tasks_5.completion_date <= CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, service_tasks_5.taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, service_tasks_5.taskdate))), 101)) GROUP BY dbo.service_report.service_ref, country_4.ID, service_tasks_5.completion_date, service_tasks_5.taskdate, service_tasks_5.grace_val, MONTH(service_tasks_5.taskdate), YEAR(service_tasks_5.taskdate)) AS qServiceDays GROUP BY ID, Yr, Mo) AS [Service Days Country Summary] ON dashboard_report_data.Country_ID = [Service Days Country Summary].ID AND dashboard_report_data.Yr = [Service Days Country Summary].Yr AND dashboard_report_data.Mo = [Service Days Country Summary].Mo WHERE (dashboard_report_data.Country = @CountryName) ORDER BY GeoName, dashboard_report_data.Yr, dashboard_report_data.Mo

SELECT TOP (100) PERCENT Country AS GeoName, SUM([Expected Reports]) AS [YTD Expected Reports], SUM([Delivered Reports]) AS [YTD Delivered Reports], SUM([Service Visit Not Performed]) AS [Commitments Met w/o SCxx Report (Reasons)], SUM([Not Delivered]) AS [Commitments Not Delivered], SUM(Rescheduled) AS [Commitments Rescheduled] FROM (SELECT TOP (100) PERCENT SUM(dbo.service_tasks.isautotask) AS [Expected Reports], SUM(CASE WHEN completion_date <= CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) AND service_not_performed = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Delivered Reports], SUM(CASE WHEN (completion_date > CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) OR completion_date IS NULL) AND is_rescheduled = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Not Delivered], SUM(CASE WHEN completion_date <= CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) AND service_not_performed > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS [Service Visit Not Performed], SUM(CASE WHEN (completion_date > CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))) + '/8/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(DATEADD(m, 1, taskdate))), 101) OR completion_date IS NULL) AND is_rescheduled = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Rescheduled, RIGHT(CONVERT(VARCHAR(6), dbo.service_tasks.taskdate, 106), 3) + ' ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)) AS Year_Month, MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate) AS Mo, YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate) AS Yr, dbo.country.Country, dbo.country.ID AS Country_ID FROM dbo.service_tasks INNER JOIN dbo.productionfacility ON dbo.service_tasks.productionfacility_ref = dbo.productionfacility.ProductionFacilityRef INNER JOIN dbo.country ON dbo.productionfacility.service_country = dbo.country.ID WHERE (dbo.service_tasks.is_service_task = 1) AND (dbo.service_tasks.taskdate BETWEEN '1/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(GETDATE()), 101) AND DATEADD(d, - 1, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(GETDATE())) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(GETDATE())))) AND (dbo.service_tasks.taskdate + dbo.service_tasks.grace_val BETWEEN dbo.service_tasks.taskdate AND DATEADD(d, 30, CONVERT(date, CONVERT(nvarchar(2), MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)) + '/1/' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)), 101))) AND (dbo.service_tasks.isautotask = 1) AND (dbo.country.Regionref = 3) GROUP BY MONTH(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate), RIGHT(CONVERT(VARCHAR(6), dbo.service_tasks.taskdate, 106), 3) + ' ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4), YEAR(dbo.service_tasks.taskdate)), dbo.country.Country, dbo.country.ID) AS dashboard_report_data WHERE Country = @CountryName GROUP BY Country ORDER BY GeoName
